Package com.jaunt_api.component

Interface Summary
Permutable Interface for an object that can be permuted through a fixed number of states.
 

Class Summary
ButtonComponent This class represents an HTML/XHTML button that does not by default generate a name-value pair when pressed (eg, <input type='reset'>, <input type='button'>)
CheckBoxComponent This class represents an HTML/XHTML checkbox.
FieldComponent A representation of an HTML/XHTML hidden field, textfield, password field, or any other form component that supports the value attribute.
FileComponent Represents a file-selection form component.
Form A class representing a HTML/XHTML form, with methods for finding, retrieving, and setting form fields of various types (eg textfields, dropdown menus, checkboxes, hidden fields, etc), as well as methods for submitting the form and generating request permuations.
FormComponent An abstract class representing a form's component (eg textfield, radiobutton, etc).
ImageComponent Represents a form component of type image.
Meta Represents a Meta component.
OptionComponent Represents an HTML or XHTML menu option component.
RadioButtonComponent Represents an HTML/XHTML radio button component.
RadioButtonGroup Represents a group of HTML/XHTML radio button components.
SelectComponent Represents a select component (menu or dropdown menu) in a Form.
TextAreaComponent Represents an HTML/XHTML textarea form component (<textarea>).
